MOONBLADE

        Available to all Lunar magi are the mystical MoonBlades
        in the Lunar forge below the Guild.  The smithy Clifnord
        forges them of mithril and magic to the Lunar magi's
        exact specifications.  They may only be used while Lunar powers
        are active, but will never restrict Lunar powers.  All other
        guild restrictions apply.  Clifnord demands a modest charge for
        the use of the MoonBlades, but also gives partial recompensation
        to the Lunar who returns a Blade to him in working order.

COST: Monetary -- Varies.   GL: Any.
